nhc_headline: ...PRISCILLA EXPECTED TO BECOME A LARGE HURRICANE IN THE NEXT DAY OR SO...
summary: ...PRISCILLA EXPECTED TO BECOME A LARGE HURRICANE IN THE NEXT DAY OR SO... As of 5:00 AM MST Sun Oct 05 the center of Priscilla was located near 16.3, -106.9 with movement NNW at 5 mph. The minimum central pressure was 991 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 65 mph.
